The end of 2022 marks 6 years of completed daily fitness goals 🏁⁣
⁣
2017: Workout/Active everyday ⁣
2018: Run a minimum of 1 mile⁣
2019: Virtual Yoga class⁣
2020: Swim, Bike or Run + 100 air squats ⁣
2021: 21 minutes of planks + 10k steps⁣
2022: Burpees & crunches amount = the day of the year + 10 minutes of stretching ⁣
